      "justification": "If confirmed, this means the research was motivated by informal observations rather than systematic evidence. The paper is transparent about this limitation and calls for proper validation, so it doesn't invalidate the theoretical contributions but does highlight the need for empirical follow-up."
    }
  ]
}
